---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<MainLayout title="Utopia Studio | Home">
    <div class="fixed top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-125 h-125 bg-[#0F393D] rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-10 z-0"></div>
    <div class="fixed bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-100 h-100 bg-[#14b8a6] rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-5 z-0"></div>

    <main id="home-content" class="relative z-10 min-h-screen max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 flex flex-col items-center">
        
        <h2 class="text-center font-light tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-gold opacity-90 mb-20 text-xl md:text-2xl">What is Utopia studio?</h2>
        <div class="mb-16 w-full bg-[#111111]/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[50px_10px_50px_10px] flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center overflow-hidden border border-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(15,57,61,0.3)]">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-14">
                <div class="rounded-[40px_10px_40px_10px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/5">
                    <img src="/whatwebsite.png" alt="Utopia Studio Interior" class="w-full h-auto" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                 <h3 class="font-light text-xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight text-white uppercase">
                    A SPACE TO EXPLORE YOUR <span class="text-gold italic font-medium">CREATIVITY</span> <br/>
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm tracking-[0.3em]">DIGITAL & PHYSICAL ART</span>
                 </h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-sm md:text-base">
                  Utopia is more than a workspace; it is a movement. We designed this environment to silence the noise of the outside world, allowing creators and non-creators to focus entirely whether it is on the precision of their craft or learning new skills to achieve excellence. Every corner is built for inspiration, development and focus.
                 </p>
                 <div class="mt-8 h-px w-16 bg-gold/40"></div>     
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-center font-light tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-gold opacity-90 mb-10 text-xl md:text-2xl">Why Utopia studio?</h2>
        <div class="mt-10 mb-16 w-full bg-[#111111]/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[50px_10px_50px_10px] flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center overflow-hidden border border-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(15,57,61,0.3)]">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-14">
                <div class="rounded-[40px_10px_40px_10px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/5">
                    <img src="/whywebsite.png" alt="Utopia Studio Interior" class="w-full h-auto" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                 <h3 class="font-light text-xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight text-white uppercase">
                    UTOPIA'S CREATION IN A <span class="text-gold italic font-medium">NUTSHELL</span> <br/>
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm tracking-[0.3em]"> PASSION & AMBITION</span>
                 </h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-sm md:text-base">
                  Utopia is born from a seed planted from the community. A seed that grew and expanded into whole new "tree" for the development of whoever wants to evolve. We took care of it and now it's time to harvest the fruits that will go back to the community. This way the cirlce closes and continues to grow stronger. 
                 </p>
                 <div class="mt-8 h-px w-16 bg-gold/40"></div>     
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="mt-20 text-center font-light tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-gold opacity-90 mb-20 text-xl md:text-2xl">How we chose UTOPIA?</h2>
        <div class="mb-16 w-full bg-[#111111]/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[50px_10px_50px_10px] flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center overflow-hidden border border-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(15,57,61,0.3)]">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 p-6 md:p-14">
                <div class="rounded-[40px_10px_40px_10px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/5">
                    <img src="/howwebsite.png" alt="Utopia Studio Interior" class="w-full h-auto" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
                 <h3 class="font-light text-xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight text-white uppercase">
                    MEANING BEYOND <span class="text-gold italic font-medium">WORDS</span> <br/>
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm tracking-[0.3em]">CORE VALUES OVER RECOGNITION</span>
                 </h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide text-sm md:text-base">
                    Briefly speaking, Utopia means "perfect place". It represents a vision of a world where all people can live in harmony. We chose this name because it reflects our goal to create that "ideal" space where creativity, collaboration, and personal growth can be achieved without limitations. Utopia Studio is our responsibility for creating an environment where individuals can pursue their passions and reach their full potential.
                 </p>
                 <div class="mt-8 h-px w-16 bg-gold/40"></div>     
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div id="cursor" class="fixed w-8 h-8 border border-gold rounded-full pointer-events-none z-9999 transition-transform duration-100 ease-out mix-blend-difference hidden md:block"></div>
</MainLayout>

<script>
    const cursor = document.getElementById('cursor') as HTMLElement;
    document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
        if(cursor) {
            cursor.style.transform = `translate(${e.clientX - 16}px, ${e.clientY - 16}px)`;
        }
    });

    const links = document.querySelectorAll('a, button');
    links.forEach(link => {
        link.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
            if(cursor) cursor.style.transform += ' scale(2)';
        });
        link.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
            if(cursor) cursor.style.transform = cursor.style.transform.replace(' scale(2)', '');
        });
    });
</script>